      "title": "Strict surveillance around the Parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the Parliament is scheduled to meet at 10.00 this morning, a massive search operation has been started by the security forces in the surrounding area.",
        "Sri Lanka Army Police Police Special Task Force and nearly a thousand police personnel have been deployed for that purpose.",
        "A number of security checkpoints have also been set up on the main roads leading to the Parliament and checks have been increased."
      ],
